title: mother's pancakes

needs:
 - ¼ pt milk
 - ¼ pt natural yoghurt
 - 1oz melted butter
 - egg
 - 2tbsp caster sugar
 - 5oz plain flour
 - 2tsp baking powder
 - ½ tsp salt

steps:
 - blend together the milk, yoghurt, butter, egg, and sugar.
 - sift together flour, baking powder, and salt.
 - blend the milk mix into the flour mix.
